CompanyName.value: Nuveen New Jersey Quality Municipal Income Fund

CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Nuveen New Jersey Quality Municipal Income Fund is an asset management company. The Fund invests in municipal securities that are exempt from federal and New Jersey state income taxes. The Fund invests at least 80% of its managed assets in securities rated, at the time of investment, investment grade (Baa/BBB or better by S&P, Moodys, or Fitch) or, if they are unrated, are judged by the manager to be of comparable quality.
